## Usage Restrictions

This project uses NLLB-200 (No Language Left Behind) translation model from Meta AI which is licensed under the CC-BY-NC 4.0 (Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International) license. Therefore:

1. **Non-Commercial Use Only**: This application may only be used for non-commercial purposes. Commercial use of this application, particularly the translation functionality powered by NLLB-200, is not permitted without obtaining a separate license from Meta AI.

2. **Attribution**: If you use this project in your work, please provide appropriate attribution to:
   - This project
   - [OpenAI Whisper](https://github.com/openai/whisper)
   - [Meta AI's NLLB-200](https://github.com/facebookresearch/fairseq/tree/nllb)
   - Other included open-source components

## Third-Party Licenses

This project incorporates several third-party open-source components, each with its own license:

- **OpenAI Whisper**: MIT License
