Please refer to the respective projects for the full text of their licenses.

## Commercial Use

For commercial use of this application, you would need to:

1. Replace the NLLB-200 translation model with an alternative translation solution that permits commercial use, or
2. Obtain a commercial license for NLLB-200 from Meta AI.

After addressing the above, you can use the codebase commercially under the MIT License terms.
